                    </div>
                    <span>This seminal work lacks badly both a focus and a meaningful content.<BR>The coverage of your needs as a programmer is takes a rather thin chapter. <BR>IMHO - one should better read the GNU Emacs and Xemacs manuals.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">good only as an intro</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
