                    </div>
                    <span>This is good as an intro book. For expert users, check out the Emacs LISP reference and tutorial avail on GNU site. Too much words for an intro book though... new users can quickly get lost in the sea of terms. The glossary is not nearly as complete.</span>
                  
              
